15. **Kenetova, R. B., Dzuganova, L. M., Ordokova, F. M., Abregova, A. V., & Abazova, K. V. (2022).** *Sociolinguistic Approach and Gender Studies in Linguistics.* Journal of Positive School Psychology, Vol. 6, No. 2, pp. 2010–2016.  
